{"id":95,"ayahs":[{"number":102,"arabic":"وَإِذَا كُنتَ فِيهِمْ فَأَقَمْتَ لَهُمُ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ فَلْتَقُمْ طَآئِفَةٌۭ مِّنْهُم مَّعَكَ وَلْيَأْخُذُوٓا۟ أَسْلِحَتَهُمْ فَإِذَا سَجَدُوا۟ فَلْيَكُونُوا۟ مِن وَرَآئِكُمْ وَلْتَأْتِ طَآئِفَةٌ أُخْرَىٰ لَمْ يُصَلُّوا۟ فَلْيُصَلُّوا۟ مَعَكَ وَلْيَأْخُذُوا۟ حِذْرَهُمْ وَأَسْلِحَتَهُمْ ۗ وَدَّ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَوْ تَغْفُلُونَ عَنْ أَسْلِحَتِكُمْ وَأَمْتِعَتِكُمْ فَيَمِيلُونَ عَلَيْكُم مَّيْلَةًۭ وَٰحِدَةًۭ ۚ وَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْكُمْ إِن كَانَ بِكُمْ أَذًۭى مِّن مَّطَرٍ أَوْ كُنتُم مَّرْضَىٰٓ أَن تَضَعُوٓا۟ أَسْلِحَتَكُمْ ۖ وَخُذُوا۟ حِذْرَكُمْ ۗ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ أَعَدَّ لِلْكَٰفِرِينَ عَذَابًۭا مُّهِينًۭا","translation":"Thus, when thou art among the believers and about to lead them in prayer, let [only] part of them stand up with thee, retaining their arms. Then, after they have finished their prayer, let them provide you cover while another group, who have not yet prayed, shall come forward and pray with thee, being fully prepared against danger and retaining their arms: (for) those who are bent on denying the truth would love to see you oblivious of your arms and your equipment, so that they might fall upon you in a surprise attack. But it shall not be wrong for you to lay down your arms [while you pray] if you are troubled by rain or if you are ill; but [always] be fully prepared against danger. Verily, God has readied shameful suffering for all who deny the truth!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/595.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":72026,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং (হে নবী) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72027,"position":2,"arabic":"كُنتَ","translation":"তুমি হও","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72028,"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهِمْ","translation":"তাদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72029,"position":4,"arabic":"فَأَقَمْتَ","translation":"তুমি অতঃপর কায়েম করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72030,"position":5,"arabic":"لَهُمُ","translation":"তাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72031,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ","translation":"সলাত","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72032,"position":7,"arabic":"فَلْتَقُمْ","translation":"দাঁড়ায় যেন তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72033,"position":8,"arabic":"طَآئِفَةٌۭ","translation":"একদল","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72034,"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنْهُم","translation":"তাদের মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72035,"position":10,"arabic":"مَّعَكَ","translation":"তোমার সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72036,"position":11,"arabic":"وَلْيَأْخُذُوٓا۟","translation":"এবং তারা যেন রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72037,"position":12,"arabic":"أَسْلِحَتَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের অস্ত্র (তাদের কাছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72038,"position":13,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72039,"position":14,"arabic":"سَجَدُوا۟","translation":"তারা সিজদা করে ফেলে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72040,"position":15,"arabic":"فَلْيَكُونُوا۟","translation":"তারা তখন হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72041,"position":16,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72042,"position":17,"arabic":"وَرَآئِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের পিছনে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72043,"position":18,"arabic":"وَلْتَأْتِ","translation":"এবং আসে যেন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72044,"position":19,"arabic":"طَآئِفَةٌ","translation":"দল","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72045,"position":20,"arabic":"أُخْرَىٰ","translation":"অন্য (যারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72046,"position":21,"arabic":"لَمْ","translation":"নাই","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72047,"position":22,"arabic":"يُصَلُّوا۟","translation":"সলাত পড়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72048,"position":23,"arabic":"فَلْيُصَلُّوا۟","translation":"তারা পড়ে যেন তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72049,"position":24,"arabic":"مَعَكَ","translation":"তোমার সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72050,"position":25,"arabic":"وَلْيَأْخُذُوا۟","translation":"ও তারাও রাখে যেন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72051,"position":26,"arabic":"حِذْرَهُمْ","translation":"সতর্কতা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72052,"position":27,"arabic":"وَأَسْلِحَتَهُمْ ۗ","translation":"ও তাদের অস্ত্রশস্ত্র (তাদের কাছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72054,"position":28,"arabic":"وَدَّ","translation":"কামনা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72055,"position":29,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72056,"position":30,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"কুফরী করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72057,"position":31,"arabic":"لَوْ","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72058,"position":32,"arabic":"تَغْفُلُونَ","translation":"গাফিল হও তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72059,"position":33,"arabic":"عَنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72060,"position":34,"arabic":"أَسْلِحَتِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের অস্ত্রশস্ত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/004_102_035.mp3","charTypeNa